= coldfusion-hoptoad-notifier

* http://wiki.github.com/shayne/coldfusion-hoptoad-notifier
* http://github.com/shayne/coldfusion-hoptoad-notifier/tree/master
* http://github.com/shayne/coldfusion-hoptoad-notifier/issues
* http://coldfusionhoptoadnotifier.riaforge.org/

== DESCRIPTION:

A simple ColdFusion CFC that sends errors and exceptions to Hoptoad

== SUPPORT:

The bug tracker is available here:

  * http://github.com/shayne/coldfusion-hoptoad-notifier/issues

== SYNOPSIS:

  #### Application.cfc
  <cffunction name="onApplicationStart" ...>
    <cfset application.HoptoadNotifier = CreateObject("component", "path.to.HoptoadNotifier").init(API_KEY) />
  </cffunction>
  
  ...
  
  <cffunction name="onError" ...>
    <cfargument name="exception" ... />
    <cfset application.HoptoadNotifier.exceptionHandler(arguments.exception) />
  </cffunction>

== REQUIREMENTS:

* ColdFusion 8+
* Java 1.5+

